The present invention discloses comprehensive railway train early warning system and its operation method. The present invention works in frequency channel dissimilar to that for train scheduling signal, and has no problems of co-channel interference, radio train scheduling signal cross-talk and weak field signal covering by strong region. The system of the present invention can be used in railway multiple track and other sections with poor radio transmission condition. In addition, the railway train early warning system can send various early warning information and alarm information in broadcast mode, and may receive warning information along the line to avoid running accident and raise safety.

